openmediavault-uartdisplay (1.0.0-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  - UART display daemon for NAS status monitoring
  - Support for mdadm RAID arrays
  - Support for btrfs filesystems
  - Configurable UART settings (device, baudrate)
  - 10-second update interval
  - Systemd service integration

